si.t: Note: Change this to your target value
On the 'Latency Data sheet', be sure to delete/insert rows above the black bar above to keep all the data ranges intact
On the 'Latency and Ops Graph' sheet, the X-Axis minimum value must be manualy set. Excel will set the X axis value to 0 if you try and automatically have Excel calculate the value
On the 'Latency and Ops Graph' sheet, you can check and uncheck the different toggle boxes to display/hide the various features
You need to set your desired max latency in 'Latency and Ops Graph' cell D2 when checking that box
